Oroplata Resources Inc: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback
















oroplata resources inc
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Materials
Industry: Metals & Mining
Sub-Industry: Other Mined Minerals
Oroplata Resources, Inc. operates as a mineral exploration company. The Company focuses on acquisition, exploration, and development of mineral properties. Oroplata Resources conducts business in the Dominican Republic.




