Company – Lithortech Resources Inc.





































































 





 
























THE COMPANYAbout Lithortech Resources Inc.

Lithortech Resources, Inc., a wholly owned subsidiary of Oroplata Resources, Inc., is a lithium resource explorer and developer, with a primary focus on becoming a low cost provider for the flourishing lithium battery industry. Through steady-handed management and keen attention to market conditions, we have acquired a number of lithium resources throughout the West Nevada region. The ultimate goal of our operation is to local, develop and supply lithium to key buyers like Tesla, Tesla, Faraday, Panasonic, AESC, LG, BYD and even utility companies.The world is in the midst of a revolution. Every day, the number of fossil fuels on the planet grows smaller and smaller. This necessitates the transition to sustainable energy sources, particularly in the automotive (car) sector. Companies like Tesla are rapidly gaining market share in this fast growing industry. However, these innovators will need access to large amounts of lithium for the batteries that make their vehicles run. As the owner of some of the richest Lithium mines in the country, Lithortech is perfectly positioned to be a leading supplier of raw materials to this fast-growing industry.Lithortech Resources also has one of the largest land packages in Nevada covering over 20,000 acres. The land package is highly prospective and close to the only producing lithium operation in North America – Silver Peak, owned and operated by Albemarle, one the world’s largest lithium producers.
Oroplata Resources Inc., our parent company, is listed on the OTCBB under the symbol ORRP.
